The sawdust is not thrown out at the end of the season, so they may end up in tea.
"Moreover, the bags do not always include tea plants," Tikhonova said.
According to her, it is better to abandon the use of such a drink in favor of tea for weight loss, which is sold in specialized stores.
In addition, she stressed that the danger of packaged tea lies not only in the composition, but also in the method of its production - the microparticles are heated to high temperatures, due to which they can begin to release harmful substances.
“It is best to buy pure green or black tea – such a drink will have the least additives,” said the expert.
