By 2023, the first school of the new format will open in the center of the capital
The new school will be opened in Hamovniks.
According to the head of the Moskomstroyinvest Anastasia Pyatova, there will create all conditions for self-realization and development of children’s talents.
The educational institution decided to call it a "New Look".
This project will be supervised by the Moscow State Institute of International Relations of the Russian Foreign Ministry and the Foundation "Economic Development of Higher School".
The design of the building with an area of about 10,000 "squares" is planned to begin next year.
